===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro}} {{term|substance|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|la}} {{term|substantia||substance, essence|lang=la}}, from {{term|substans|substāns|lang=la}}, present active participle of {{term|substo|substō|exist; literally, stand under|lang=la}}, from {{term|sub|lang=la}} + {{term|sto|stō|stand|lang=la}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{audio|en-us-substance.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# Physical matter; material.
# The [[essential]] part of anything; the most vital part.
# Considerable wealth or resources.
#: ''A man of '''substance'''.''
# [[drug|Drugs]] {{gloss|illegal narcotics}}
#: '''''substance''' abuse''

